            <h1>ENGR. ANTHONY ODOGBO</h1>
            <h2>Chief Executive Officer</h2>
            
            <p>Anthony Odogbo is an Engineer , businessman, and administrator with over 24yrs experience in the Oil and Gas industry. He is the CEO of trackzone energy resources Ltd.</p>
            
            <p>He attended the St. John/Mary’s Unity Secondary School in Ondo State. He obtained a higher national diploma in geological engineering at the Federal Polytechnic Ado Ekiti and later obtained a B.Tech in Chemical Engineering in LAUTECH. Bagged a Masters degree in Petroleum Engineering at the University of Benin. He also holds a Masters in Business Administration (MBA) from the University of Leicester, United Kingdom.</p>
            
            <p>Anthony Odogbo started his career as a Youth corper with the Pipeline & Product Marketing Company (PPMC) a subsidiary of the NNPC as a Chemical Engineer. In 2000, he joined Global Gas & Refining as Operations Team Lead. He joined the Shell Petroleum Development Company in 2002 and serve in different in the Production Operations team before joining Seven Exploration and Production Company OML 13 in 2012 as pioneer staff that developed, commissioned and managed the 200MMSCFD Central Processing Facility with other adjourning facilities. In 2016, he then joined Energia Ltd and managed the day to day operations of the OML 56 as Ag. Chief Technical Officer for 9yrs.</p>
            
            <p>He is recognized for his transformative leadership, strategic vision, and operational excellence. He has a proven track record in orchestrating company-wide operational overhaul, project management, production optimization, implementing data driven decision, making proceses and managing cross functional team.</p>
            <p>He is a member Nigeria Society of Engineers (NSE), Council for the Regulation of Engineering in Nigeria (COREN), Society of Petroleum Engineers (SPE), Nigeria Gas Association (NGA), Nigeria Institute of Safety Professionals (NISP), and Project Management Professionals (PMP).</p>
